bodylog.logic

Class Move

  • java.lang.Object
    • bodylog.logic.abstracts.VariableList
      • bodylog.logic.Move
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Move>

    public class Move
extends VariableList
implements Comparable<Move>
    The first component in the logical hierarchy. Container for session data and movement variables. Contains a name, a list of Variables and a list of Sessions. The name is used as the name of the statistics directory and the move defining file, from which it is also read.
    See Also:
    VariableList, Variable, Session, Set
